div.font:
Pack square/cube fully with squares/cubes.
No movement possible.
Can never pack square/cube fully with circles/spheres,
there will always be space between.
Circles/spheres can move within the space of the square,
whereas squares/cubes will move with much greater difficulty
if at all. Circles/spheres, even when fully packing a square/cube,
can still rotate along any of their axes, whereas a square in such
a situation would not be able to move at all.
